- **Supply Chain**: $1.2 billion annual savings
- **Energy & Resources**: $800 million annual savings
- **Quality & Waste**: $400 million annual savings
- **Total Cost Savings**: $5.2 billion annually

### ROI Calculation
```
Total Benefits = Revenue Impact + Cost Savings
Total Benefits = $7.3B + $5.2B = $12.5B annually

ROI = (Annual Benefits - Annual Investment) / Annual Investment × 100%
ROI = ($12.5B - $2.4B) / $2.4B × 100%
ROI = $10.1B / $2.4B × 100%
ROI = 421% annually

Cumulative ROI over 18 months = 1,000%+
```

